## Getting Started

{% if use_npm %}
### With npm

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev
```
{% else %}
### Without npm

Simply open `index.html` in your browser, or use a local server:

```bash
# Python 3
python -m http.server 3000

# Then open http://localhost:3000
```
{% endif %}

